Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of learning analytics and educational data mining to enhance the teaching and learning process in an educational institution. This topic falls under the category of machine learning and data mining, which is covered by cs.LG. The paper also discusses the collection and analysis of data, which could fall under the category of computer engineering (cs.CE). The use of data to predict future performance and identify risk could also fall under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses feature selection techniques, which could fall under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL) or cybernetics (cs.CY).
